# Project Architecture

- Keep business rules in `src/modules/game/domain`.
- Keep persistence and external SDK access in `src/modules/game/infrastructure`.
- Keep React composition in `src/modules/game/application` or feature hooks.
- UI components must receive data and callbacks; they must not import repositories, storage services, Supabase clients, or browser persistence directly.
- Prefer mapping external data into existing domain types instead of leaking transport/database rows through the app.
- Preserve the public shape of `TriviaSession` unless a migration plan and tests are included.
